OL,3,CSuicide figures rising in the south of
OL,4,CScotland
OL,6,FStatistics released by the National
OL,7,FRecords of Scotland have shown that
OL,8,Fthe number of people dying by suicide
OL,9,Fin the country is on the rise.
OL,11,FThe statistics comparing 2023 with
OL,12,F2022 have showcased that the number of
OL,13,Fpeople dying by suicide has increased.
OL,15,FIn Scotland, 792 people died by
OL,16,Fsuicide and increase of 30 compared to
OL,17,Fthe previous year.
