OL,6,FChildline is for anyone under 19. They
OL,7,Fhave trained counsellors on hand to
OL,8,Fhelp with any problem, at any time.
OL,10,FYou can call them on 0800 1111 at any
OL,11,Ftime. They also have a 1-2-1
OL,12,Fcounsellor chat online.
OL,14,FThe Silver Line
OL,16,FThis is a service for older people.
OL,17,FThey offer information and advice and
OL,18,Falso have a 'friendship call' service.
OL,20,FYou can contact them 24 hours a day on
OL,21,F0800 470 80 90.
